{
    "chapter": [
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "Did the story of the overwhelming come to you"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "On that day (some) faces are humble"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "working hard, exhausted"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "entering (and burning in) a scorching fire"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "they are made to drink from a boiling spring"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "There is no food for them except from a thorny plant"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "that does not nourish and it does not satisfy hunger"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "On that day (other) faces are delightful"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "pleased with their effort"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "in an excellent garden"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "they do not hear any useless talk in it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "a running spring in it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "raised sofas in it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "and drinking glasses set in place"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "and pillows arranged in rows"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "and spread out rugs"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "Do they not look at the camel, how it is created"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "And at the sky, how it is raised"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "And at the mountain, how it is set up"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 20,
            "text": "And at the earth, how it is spread out"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 21,
            "text": "So remind (them), for you are only to remind"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 22,
            "text": "You are not an overseer for them"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 23,
            "text": "But anyone who turns away and disbelieves"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 24,
            "text": "then God punishes him with the great punishment"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "Indeed their return is to Us"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 26,
            "text": "then indeed their accounting is on Us"
        }
    ]
}